{"tid":159470,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Iphone6plus問題","createTime":"2017-03-17T04:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T16:48:54.000Z","uid":52043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8969e2bf783dcc4a46cd4f53173aa1afb468b64c","tid":159470,"uid":52043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"電話一時用到一時個mon亂跳 請問係發生咩事先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7332dd904fce3d88493227862a430c402b34644b","tid":159470,"uid":52043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">手機</span>一時用到一時個mon亂跳 請問係發生咩事先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry 手機先啱自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b3892dfa6f1311f311a5ae2167281554ea5127","tid":159470,"uid":78866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"我部iphone6都係咁，已經持續左一年左右，上網搵解決方法，發現好似係部機彎左先搞到接觸不良，e.g. 手機放褲袋嗚低身果陣屈到部機。<br />\n<br />\n我自己一直以黎既解決方法就係：<br />\n<br />\nlock機再開返，試幾次，多數小問題就會即刻冇事。但如果試左好多次都唔得，就要屈一屈部機。我屈既位係屈部機既左上角，向內屈。如果向內唔得就向外屈。多數屈完再lock機再開返幾次就會冇事。<br />\n<br />\n巴打最好避免下屈親部機/跌部機落地。<br />\n<br />\n利申：等緊8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639abd47fdfa1df39c42891e321ee8042abebc36","tid":159470,"uid":13816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"181b6ed976766b930c5abd287c90883443010201","tid":159470,"uid":1002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"手你老母機咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06fe9920dd153b9e32052ec087d871178cf96c1","tid":159470,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"Touch ic 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3148cef82350ce72b375b77ddccc1c077dfc1c","tid":159470,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n部機彎<br />\n個mon要大力㩒落去再unlock先無事"}]}